would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20defend%20266%20the%20other%20day%20if%20the%20game%20(1st%20match)%20had%20carried%20on.%20You%20know%20people%2C%20particularly%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20keep%20on%20talking%20about%20India%20having%20only%20one%20or%20two%20players.%20I%20mean%20how%20many%20players%20does%20Pakistan%20have%3F%20Particularly%20in%20the%20batting%20department.%20Apart%20from%20Babar%20who%20do%20they%20have%3F%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20questioned%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Bl6T9sZy9A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20bowling%20team%20of%20the%20opposition%20sit%20down%20and%20dissects%20their%20batting%2C%20they%20would%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20how%20to%20get%20Babar%20out.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20would%20spend%20half%20the%20time%20on%20the%20others.%20None%20of%20them%20are%20such%20that%20they%20would%20scare%20the%20bowling%20group%20of%20the%20opposition%20team.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20posted%20an%20imposing%20356%20for%202%2C%20as%20Kohli%20(122%20not%20out%20off%2094%20balls)%20and%20Rahul%20(111%20not%20out%20off%20106%20balls)%2C%20which%20was%20his%20sixth%20ODI%20hundred%2C%20pummeled%20a%20hapless%20Pakistan%2C%20whose%20chase%20ended%20at%20128%20for%208%20as%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63624-kuldeep-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20(5%2F25)%20scythed%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20century%20count%20in%20ODIs%2C%20Kohli%20now%20stands%20just%20two%20behind%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sac