9Ca%20series%20of%20objectionable%20posts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20particular%20video%20of%20Manesar%20exhorting%20people%20to%20attend%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%E2%80%99s%20(VHP)%20%3Cem%3Ejalabishek%3C%2Fem%3E%20yatra%20on%20July%2031%20and%20claiming%20he%20would%20attend%20it%20himself%20is%20often%20cited%20as%20the%20trigger%20for%20the%20communal%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yatra%20was%20to%20pass%20through%20southern%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20district%20%E2%80%93%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20only%20one%20with%20a%20Muslim%20majority%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Ewhere%20Manesar%20is%20an%20unpopular%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20his%20cow%20vigilantism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20a%20regional%20leader%20in%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20which%20is%20the%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20youth%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20Manesar%20was%20booked%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20two%20men%20named%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%2C%20whose%20charred%20bodies%20were%20found%20near%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20said%20to%20have%20happened%20after%20accusations%20of%20cow%20smuggling%20were%20made%20against%20the%20two%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20both%20Rajasthan%20and%20Haryana%20have%20said%20in%20the%20past%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66380406%5C%22%3Ethey%20did%20not%20know%20Manesar%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20he%20has%20appeared%20in%20multiple%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20since%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20his%20transfer%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20from%20their%20Haryana%20counterparts%20will%20depend%20on%20court%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VHP%20%3C