he%20case%20of%20Ukraine.%20The%20war%20waged%20by%20Russia%20since%20February%202022%20receives%20only%20a%20short%20passage%2C%20distinctly%20lower%20down%20on%20the%20statement%20issued%20at%20the%20previous%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20Bali%20declaration%20and%20the%20New%20Delhi%20one%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20nonchalantly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbali-was-bali-and-new-delhi-is-new-delhi-jaishankar-on-reference-to-ukraine-in-g-20-declaration%2Farticle67289990.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522With%2520regard%2520to%2520the%2520comparison%2Cthings%2520have%2520happened%2520since%2520then.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CBali%20is%20Bali%20and%20New%20Delhi%20is%20New%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20French%20newspaper%20also%20called%20the%20declaration%20a%20disappointment%20on%20the%20climate%20front.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20disappointment%20is%20just%20as%20great%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20combating%20climate%20change.%20Despite%20the%20recent%20devastating%20succession%20of%20climate%20tragedies%2C%20the%20final%20statement%20fails%20to%20mention%20the%20objective%20of%20phasing%20out%20fossil%20fuels.%20Yet%20scientists%20consider%20this%20to%20be%20the%20only%20response%20capable%20of%20reversing%20a%20destructive%20curve%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcivil-society-calls-out-g20-declarations-omission-of-civic-space-erosion-democracy-decline%5C%22%3ECivil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20outcome%20obviously%20reflects%20India%E2%80%99s%20rigid%20determination%20not%20to%20take%20sides%20in%20the%20war%2C%20but%20it%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20countries%20at%20the%20G20%20that%20do%20oppose%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20of%20conquest%20were%20so%20prepared%20to%20be%20muzzled%20by%20the%20minority%20that%20%5Bthey%5D%20prefer%20to%20look%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20UK%20official%20said%20the%20joint%20declaration%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20weak%2C%20was%20in%20fact%20effective%20at%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%98By%20achieving%20consensus%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20G20%20has%20forced%20%5BVladimir%5D%20Putin%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20attacks%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20troops%20and%20to%20the%20return%20of%20territory%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20said.%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fsep%2F10%2Fwatered-down-g20-statement-on-ukraine-is-sign-of-indias-growing-influence%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGuardian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20summit%20was%20marked%20by%20another%20disappointment%2C%20though%20this%20one%20was%20less%20global%20in%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20word%20spread%20that%20%5BModi%5D%20was%20to%20address%20the%203%2C000%20journalists%20at%20the%20G20%20media%20centre%20late%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20ripple%20of%20excitement%20spread%20through%20the%20venue.%20TV%20broadcasters%20started%20dedicating%20live%20coverage%20to%20showing%20an%20empty%20walkway%20where%20Mr%20Modi%20might%20emerge%20at%20%E2%80%98any%20moment%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shweta%20Sharma%20wrote%20for%20UK%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Findia%2Fmodi-media-g20-india-press-freedom-b2409090.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndependent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20was%20not%20true%20as%20Modi%20simply%20waved%20and%20walked%20past%20the%20journalists%20who%20had%20waited%20for%20over%20three%20hours%20in%20hopes%20of%20what%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20the%20first%20press%20conference%20Modi%20held%20in%20his%20nine%20years%20as%20prime%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CJournalists%20shouted%20questions%20as%20simple%20as%20%E2%80%98Was%20the%20G20%20successful%20sir%3F%E2%80%99%20but%20the%20prime%20minister%20just%20waved%20silently%20and%20left%2C%20as%20some%20members%20of%20the%20crowd%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20unclear%20what%20media%20organisations%20they%20represented%20%E2%80%93%20began%20patriotic%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20mata%20ki%20ja%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ei%E2%80%99%20(Long%20live%20Mother%20India).%20In%20the%20end%20this%20was%20not%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20press%20but%20rather%20a%20victory%20lap%20for%20a%20prime%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694520042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12151520%2FCopy-of-Lead-image-size-3.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fglobal-media-highlights-watered-down-statement-on-russia-ukraine-after-modis-g20-pr-push%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France%E2%80%99s%20Le%20Monde%20called%20the%20event%20%E2%80%9Cprofitable%20for%20the%20organiser%E2%80%9D%20but%20said%20that%20the%20summit%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20little%20to%20mask%20the%20disappointment%20of%20the%20final%20statement%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fglobal-media-highlights-watered-down-statement-on-russia-ukraine-after-modis-g20-pr-push%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin