previous%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20from%20July%202015%20to%20December%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20lodged%20against%20Yadav%20at%20Mungra%20Badshahpur%20police%20station%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20Chandresh%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20village%20headman%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20local%20mandal%20adhyaksh.%20Yadav%2C%20a%201983-batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%2C%20was%20booked%20under%20Sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%2C%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircle%20officer%20Machhlishahr%2C%20Atar%20Singh%2C%20said%20as%20per%20the%20complaint%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20officials%20of%20the%20revenue%20team%20and%20chakbandi%20department%20had%20gathered%20in%20the%20secretariat%20of%20the%20gram%20sabha%20Tarahati%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%20to%20settle%20land%20disputes%20and%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarahati%20is%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%20where%20his%20mother%20served%20as%20a%20former%20gram%20pradhan%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20September%2011%2C%20when%20local%20villagers%20led%20by%20headman%20Gupta%20were%20raising%20their%20grievances%20with%20revenue%20officials%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Etehsildar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Elekhpal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20local%20SHO%2C%20and%20others%2C%20Yadav%20barged%20into%20the%20hall%2C%20alleged%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20when%20he%20saw%20Yadav%20he%20got%20up%20from%20his%20chair%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%20but%20Yadav%20insulted%20him%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20hall%20after%20knowing%20his%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20got%20all%20fired%20up%2C%20grabbed%20my%20collar%20and%20struck%20me%20twice%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20panchayat%20bhavan%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20Gupta%20in%20his%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Gupta%20accused%20Yadav%20and%20his%20family%20of%20illegally%20grabbing%20village%20land%2C%20including%20the%20land%20of%20the%20gram%20sabha%2C%20land%20of%20a%20local%20girls%E2%80%99%20school%20and%20barren%20patches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20illegally%20grabbed%20a%20lot%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village%20and%20the%20villagers%20were%20in%20the%20panchayat%20bhavan%20to%20raise%20their%20complaints%20when%20Yadav%20showed%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20any%20personal%20enmity%20or%20dispute%20with%20Yadav%2C%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20only%20met%20him%20once%20before%20this%2C%20when%20his%20brother%20had%20expired.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircle%20officer%20Singh%20said%20the%20matter%20was%20being%20probed.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20with%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160828%2FThe-Wire-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-registers-fir-against-ex-dgp-jagmohan-yadav-for-allegedly-attacking-bjp-leader%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yadav%20served%20as%20the%20DGP%20under%20the%20previous%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20headed%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20from%20July%20to%20December%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-registers-fir-against-ex-dgp-jagmohan-yadav-for-allegedly-attacking-bjp-leader%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Govt's%20Statement%20Against%20Security%20Forces%20Goes%20Against%20Its%20Own%20Police's%20Version%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-