2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20calibrated%20response%20in%20self-defence%20and%20to%20control%20the%20unruly%20mob%2C%20security%20forces%20used%20minimum%20force%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob%20that%20led%20to%20injuries%20to%20a%20few%20persons%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20mob%20out%20of%20which%20two%20reportedly%20died.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20noted%20that%20the%20firing%20had%20been%20against%20%E2%80%9Carmed%20miscreants%20who%20attempted%20to%20resort%20to%20arson%20and%20violence%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20statement%20highlighted%20that%20cops%20were%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjoint%20operation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20statement%20of%20condemnation%20mentioned%20only%20central%20security%20forces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20state%20home%20ministry%2C%20held%20by%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20contains%20details%20gleaned%20from%20sources%20who%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20had%20resorted%20to%20firing%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20exhausting%20all%20options%20to%20break%20up%20the%20huge%20crowd%2C%20including%20requests%20to%20them%20to%20disperse%20followed%20by%20a%20baton-charge%2C%20tear%20gas%20shelling%2C%20the%20firing%20of%20rubber%20bullets%2C%20and%20then%20the%20firing%20of%20bullets%20below%20the%20waist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20growing%20division%20between%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20calm%20in%20the%20state%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-violence-imphal-media-army-letter-editors-guild%5C%22%3Ereflected%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Army%20wrote%20to%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20local%20media%20supporting%20one%20community%20over%20the%20other%2C%20and%20worsening%20the%20strife%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%2C%20publicised%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20assumes%20significance%20as%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20is%C2%A0facing%20a%20first%20information%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20against%20it%20over%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20it%20released%20on%20the%20news%20environment%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-security-forces-army-police-cabinet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'Telegraph'%20report%20notes%20how%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20and%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20differing%20versions%20of%20gunfight%20between%20an%20armed%20group%20and%20the%20security%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple's%20iPhone%2015%20Launch%20Clouded%20By%20China%20Problems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20expected%20to%20unveil%20a%20new%20iPhone%2015%20lineup%20as%20questions%20about%20market%20access%20in%20China%20and%20competition%20hang%20over%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20listed%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%20made%20up%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Apple's%20%24394.3%20billion%20in%20sales%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it%20faces%20new%20challenges%20with%20selling%20in%20China%2C%20the%20Cupertino%2C%20California%20firm's%20third-largest%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20latest%20phones%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20new%20charging%20ports%2C%20titanium%20cases%2C%20and%20cameras%2C%20but%20their%20debut%20at%20its%20Apple%20Park%20headquarters%20at%2010%20am%20PT%20(1700%20GMT)%20will%20come%20as%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20expanded%20some%20restrictions%20on%20using%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20will%20also%20have%20to%20grapple%20with%20competition%20from%20Huawei%20Technologies%2C%20which%20was%20its%20top%20rival%20in%20China's%20premium%20smartphone%20market%20until%20US%20export%20controls%20ruined%20Huawei's%20phone%20business%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Huawei%20started%20selling%20the%20Mate%2060%20Pro%2C%20a%20high-end%20phone%20that%20uses%20Chinese-made%20chips%20that%20some%20US%20lawmakers%20believe%20were%20manufactured%20in%20violation%20of%20US%20trade%20curbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuawei%20wants%20to%20gain%20an%20edge%20over%20Apple%20with%20add-on%20features%20like%20satellite%20calling%20that%20relies%20on%20China's%20government-backed%20network.%20Apple's%20current%20iPhone%20lineup%20includes%20satellite%20capabilities%2C%20though%20they%20are%20meant%20only%20for%20emergency%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20iphone%2015%20Launch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20its%20new%20product%20lineup.%20By%20far%20the%20biggest%20change%20for%20most%20Apple%20customers%20will%20be%20a%20switch%20from%20Apple's%20propriety%20%26quot%3BLightning%26quot%3B%20charging%20cables%20to%20USB-C%2C%20a%20standard%20that%20Apple%20already%20uses%20on%20its%20laptops%20and%20some%20high-end%20iPads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20was%20forced%20into%20the%20change%20by%20European%20regulations%2C%20but%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20company%20will%20position%20the%20change%20as%20an%20upgrade%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20faster%20data%20speeds%20that%20can%20transfer%20high-quality%20videos%20made%20with%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20are%20also%20expecting%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bperiscope%26quot%3B%20camera%20technology%20that%20could%20give%20phones%20better%20zoom%20capabilities%20and%20titanium%20cases%2C%20as%20well%20as%20upgraded%20chips.%20Such%20%26quot%3Bperiscope%26quot%3B%20lenses%20can%20use%20mirrors%20or%20prisms%20to%20get%20a%20longer%20lens%20without%20having%20to%20make%20the%20camera%20module%20much%20larger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20question%20of%20the%20day%20will%20be%20whether%20Apple%20reserves%20those%20features%20for%20a%20new%20top-end%20device%20and%20makes%20smaller%20upgrades%20to%20its%20cheaper%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20like%20we%20saw%20people%20who%20aren't%20Ultra%20athletes%20buy%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Ultra%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20buy%20this%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20camera%20or%20photography%20enthusiasts%2C%20just%20because%20they%20like%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ben%20Bajarin%2C%20chief%20executive%20and%20principal%20analyst%20of%20Creative%20Strategies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20by%20itself%20creates%20that%20buzz%20and%20momentum%20and%20allure%20to%20the%20top%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20To%20Increase%20Avg%20Price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20the%20average%20price%20per%20phone%20sold%20to%20boost%20its%20revenue%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20it%20does%20that%20by%20raising%20prices%20across%20the%20board%20or%20just%20on%20premium%20versions.%20The%20global%20smartphone%20market%20has%20slumped%20from%20shipping%20294.5%20million%20total%20phones%20to%20268%20million%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20but%20Apple's%20shipments%20declined%20the%20least%20of%20any%20major%20smartphone%20maker%2C%20dropping%20from%2046.5%20million%20phones%20to%2045.3%20million%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Counterpoint%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20we're%20in%20a%20very%20down%20smartphone%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bob%20O'Donnell%2C%20head%20of%20TECHnalysis%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Donnell%20said%20he%20will%20also%20be%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20any%20hints%20