n%3Cp%3EBarring%20Rohit%2C%20five%20other%20Indian%20batters%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20score%2010%2C000%20runs%20in%20ODI%20cricket.%20Having%20scored%20a%20half-century%20in%20the%20last%20match%2C%20the%20Hitman%20also%20brought%20up%20his%20fifty%20in%20the%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rohit%20Sharma%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20with%20the%20team%20making%20one%20change%20with%20spin%20all-rounder%20Axar%20Patel%20coming%20in%20for%20pacer%20Shardul%20Thakur.%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20remained%20unchanged%20from%20their%20last%20match%20against%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20have%20a%20bat.%20That's%20the%20challenge%20you%20come%20across%20as%20a%20sportsman%2C%20different%20challenges%20thrown%20at%20you%20as%20a%20player%20and%20as%20a%20team.%20We%20ensured%20everyone%20got%20into%20the%20pool%20after%20the%20game%20last%20night.%20They%20are%20fresh%20as%20we%20had%20five%20days%20off%20before%20these%20two%20games.%20Last%20game%20was%20good%20for%20us%2C%20we%20batted%20well%20and%20then%20came%20out%20to%20defend%20the%20total%20with%20some%20good%20bowling.%20But%20again%20this%20is%20a%20new%20day%20and%20a%20fresh%20game.%20The%20pitch%20looks%20different%2C%20looks%20a%20lot%20drier%20and%20there's%20no%20grass%20and%20hence%20we%20bring%20in%20Axar%20for%20Shardul.%20It%20might%20assist%20the%20spinners%20but%20we%20also%20have%20three%20quality%20pacers%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20at%20the%20time%20of%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(c)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20(wk)%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESri%20Lanka%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDasun%20Shanaka%20(c)%2C%20Pathum%20Nissanka%2C%20Dimuth%20Karunar