%20measures%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-fiscally-prudent-is-delhis-aap-government-really%5C%22%3Eshown%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20for%20the%20period%202013-14%20to%202017-18%2C%20there%20was%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20public%20debt%20to%20the%20Gross%20State%20Domestic%20Product%20(GSDP)%20from%207.23%25%20to%204.89%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotwithstanding%20the%20uncritical%20political%20slandering%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20an%20argument%20can%20be%20made%20that%20an%20objective%20and%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20the%20social%20objectives%20behind%20cash%20transfers%20is%20needed%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20are%20targeted%20towards%20a%20particular%20sub-section%20such%20as%20women.%20This%20should%20be%20done%20in%20the%20light%20of%20context-specific%20realities%20of%20women%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20embedded%20in%20a%20socio-political%20and%20cultural%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analyses%20in%20the%20subsequent%20paragraphs%20will%20illuminate%20why%20affirmative%20action%20through%20cash%20transfers%20is%20a%20viable%20redistributive%20strategy%20and%20the%20specific%20role%20that%20cash%20transfers%20could%20play%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20terms%20of%20reducing%20physical%20violence%20and%20empowering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20affirmative%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20concern%20that%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FSundayapp%2FpJdRTr4eBlaCIUVMKggVDM%2FCash-transfers-Miracle-or-mirage.html%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20policy%20circles%20regarding%20cash%20transfers%20is%20that%20it%20may%20be%20a%20step%20towards%20state%20withdrawal%20from%20many%20essential%20services%20such%20as%20food%2C%20nutrition%2C%20health%2C%20and%20education.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20recently%20introduced%20welfare%20schemes%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%2C%20cash%20transfers%20through%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20is%20supplemented%20with%20in-kind%20distribution%20of%20commodities%20and%20services.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Sakthi%20scheme%20provides%20free%20transport%20to%20all%20women%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20economic%20class%2C%20to%20travel%20in%20non-premium%20state%20buses%20and%20the%20Gruha%20Jyoti%20scheme%20provides%20up%20to%20200%20units%20of%20free%20power%20to%20households%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECash%20transfers%20to%20women%20can%20also%20be%20justified%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20social%20injustices%20and%20economic%20marginalisation%20faced%20by%20women.%20The%20Global%20Gender%20Gap%20Report%202023%20shows%20that%2C%20in%20the%20criteria%20%E2%80%98Economic%20Participation%20and%20Opportunity%E2%80%99%20(includes%20indicators%20like%20labour-force%20participation%20rate%2C%20wage%20equality%20for%20similar%20work%2C%20earned%20income%20etc.)%2C%20India%20has%20achieved%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-climbs-eight-places-to-127-in-global-gender-index-says-wef-report%2Farticle66994156.ece%5C%22%3E36.7%25%20gender%20parity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20improvement%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fgender-equity-index-india-work-from-home-coronavirus-6968212%2F%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20their%20unpaid%20domestic%20and%20care%20work%20or%20when%20such%20work%20is%20made%20more%20compatible%20with%20market%20work.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fwomen-spend-7-2-hours-on-unpaid-domestic-work-compared-to-2-8-hours-spent-by-men-iima-profs-research%2Farticleshow%2F97837422.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eevidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20a%20highly%20unequal%20distribution%20of%20unpaid%20domestic%20work%20between%20men%20and%20women%2C%20with%20women%20spending%207.2%20hours%20on%20such%20work%20when%20compared%20to%20only%202.8%20hours%20spent%20by%20men%20in%20a%20day%2C%20thwarting%20attempts%20by%20women%20to%20engage%20in%20paid%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640721%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22534%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Haribai%2C%20an%20MGNREGA%20worker%20of%20Lalitpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20waits%20at%20a%20bank%20to%20collect%20her%20earnings.%20Photo%3A%20Photo%3A%20UN%20Women%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2F%20Flickr%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20such%20evidence%2C%20cash%20transfers%20can%20alleviate%20the%20distress%20of%20economic%20insecurity%20faced%20by%20women%20and%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20viable%20affirmative%20remedy.%20Besides%2C%20such%20transfers%20to%20women%20are%20also%20a%20way%20of%20creating%20discourse%20in%20the%20community%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20%E2%80%98natural%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20work%20that%20women%20do%20in%20the%20private%20sphere%20of%20the%20family%20and%20that%20housework%20also%20deserves%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20feared%20that%20unconditional%20cash%20transfers%20to%20women%20will%20re-enforce%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20keep%20women%20away%20from%20seeking%20paid%20employment%20and%20further%20entrench%20them%20in%20household%20work%20but%20such%20concerns%20are%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2022%2F26-27%2Fcommentary%2Frevaluing-unpaid-work.html%5C%22%3Emisplaced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Initiative%20for%20What%20Works%20to%20Advance%20Women%20and%20Girls%20in%20the%20Economy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwwage.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FKarnataka_Factsheet.pdf%5C%22%3E(IWWAGE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20Karnataka%20has%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20female%20labour%20force%20participation%20(LFPR)%20in%20India.%20A%20small%20transfer%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20is%20unlikely%20to%20have%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20their%20incentives%20to%20work.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwwage.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FKarnataka_Factsheet.pdf%5C%22%3Edisaggregated%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20distribution%20of%20women%20workers%20in%20Karnataka%20by%20status%20of%20employment%20reveals%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20rural%20women%20are%20engaged%20in%20self-employment%20and%20casual%20labour.%20Around%2067%25%20of%20self-employed%20women%20are%20working%20only%20as%20unpaid%20workers%20in%20family%20enterprises%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finstead-of-withdrawing-food-security-a-minimum-income-guarantee-is-needed%5C%22%3EInstead%20of%20Withdrawing%20Food%20Security%2C%20a%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Is%20Needed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20urban%20employed%20women%2C%20regular%20salaried%20jobs%20were%20most%20common%20but%20nearly%2062%25%20of%20such%20jobs%20were%20without%20any%20written%20job%20contract%20pointing%20to%20the%20precarity%20of%20such%20jobs.%20Women%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fit-is-getting-from-bad-to-worse-for-women-workers%2Farticle34574322.ece%5C%22%3Emore%20prone%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20job%20losses%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20new%20employment%20arrangements%20during%20economic%20shocks%2C%20as%20was%20observed%20during%20COVID-19.%20Hence%2C%20cash%20transfers%20can%20be%20a%20supplementary%20source%20of%20income%20to%20women%20as%20many%20are%20involved%20in%20non-paying%2C%20low-paying%20and%20precarious%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20and%20domestic%20violence%20against%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Fcash-transfers-prevent-intimate-partner-violence-study-118110600637_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cash%20transfers%20to%20women%20have%20reduced%20intimate%20partner%20violence%20(IPV)%20against%20women.%20The%20evidence%20seems%20to%20suggest%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20poverty%20and%20economic%20insecurity%20as%20triggering%20factors%20for%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%2044%25%20of%20married%20women%20have%20experienced%20spousal%20violence%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fnhfs5-survey-data-karnataka-ranks-no-1-in-domestic-violence-cases-101652076272244.html%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%20(NFHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20for%20Karnataka.%20It%20is%20the%20highest%20among%20Indian%20states.%20The%20state%20has%20also%20witnessed%20the%20highest%20increase%20in%20domestic%20violence%20from%20the%20previous%20NFHS-4%20round.%20This%20paints%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20gender-based%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20cash%20transfers%20help%20to%20reduce%20domestic%20violence%20as%20suggested%20in%20several%20studies%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20step%20forward%20towards%20gender%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20as%20pathways%20to%20women%20empowerment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnfhs-5-data-womens-empowerment%5C%22%3Eimportant%20indicator%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20among%20several%20others%2C%20is%20household%20decision-making%2C%20ranging%20from%20what%20to%20cook%2C%20when%20to%20take%20a%20child%20to%20a%20health%20centre%2C%20to%20major%20purchase%20decisions%20in%20the%20household.%20Women%20are%20economically%20empowered%20only%20if%20they%20have%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20resources.%20However%2C%20restrictive%20gender%20norms%20and%20household%20dynamics%20often%20come%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20working%20on%20an%20NREGA%20site%20building%20a%20pond%20in%20Gopalpura%2C%20Jhabua%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Credit%3A%20UN%20Woman%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-768x542.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-1024x722.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-75812%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Photo%3A%20UN%20Woman%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2FFlickr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fwomen-more-likely-to-work-if-they-can-control-their-earnings-study%2F%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Yale%20University%20analysing%20the%20empowerment%20effects%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20rights-based%20employment%20guarantee%20programme%20(MGNREGA)%2C%20showed%20that%20direct%20deposits%20of%20wages%20into%20women%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20shaping%20liberal%20attitudes%20towards%20work%20and%20in%20their%20engagement%20with%20paid%20work.%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20is%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20women%20directly%20receive%20the%20money%20into%20their%20Aadhar-linked%20bank%20accounts%2C%20thus%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20have%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-evolution-of-indias-welfare-system-2008-to-2023%5C%22%3EThe%20Evolution%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Welfare%20System%2C%202008%20to%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20recognise%20the%20potential%20role%20of%20cash%20transfers%20in%20empowering%20women%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20state%20has%20regressed%20on%20this%20front.%20There%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fblog%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-does-nfhs-5-data-tell-us-about-state-of-women-empowerment-in-india-80920%5C%22%3Edrop%20in%20the%20percentage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20ever%20married%20women%20who%20participate%20in%20household%20decisions%20(including%20health%20care%20for%20oneself%2C%20making%20major%20household%20purchases%20and%20visits%20to%20family%20or%20relatives)%20from%2082.7%25%20to%2080.4%25%20and%20Karnataka%20is%20one%20of%20the%20worst-performing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20NFHS-4%20and%20NFHS-5%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20drop%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20women%20who%20engaged%20in%20any%20form%20of%20paid%20work%20from%2037%25%20to%2029%25.%20However%2C%20women%20having%20mobile%20phones%20they%20themselves%20use%20increased%20from%2047.1%25%20to%2061.8%25.%20This%20may%20augur%20well%20for%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%2C%20provided%20adequate%20financial%20and%20digital%20literacy%20is%20provided%20to%20women%20to%20operate%20their%20mobile-linked%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20whole%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20scheme%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20is%20a%20welcome%20step.%20It%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20recognition%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20and%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20financial%20support%20would%20improve%20their%20economic%20position%2C%20enable%20them%20to%20make%20household%20decisions%20and%20participate%20in%20public%20life.%20However%2C%20this%20comes%20with%20a%20caveat.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20that%20cash%20reaches%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20women%3B%20the%20financial%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20state%20should%20ensure%20easy%20accessibility.%20As%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FState_of_Working_India_2021-One_year_of_Covid-19.pdf%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20can%20be%20rejections%20while%20accessing%20payments%20with%20no%20clear%20reason%2C%20necessitating%20multiple%20visits%20to%20banks.%20Such%20glitches%20should%20be%20avoided%20given%20that%20Indian%20women%20are%20faced%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpageturner%2Fexcerpt%2Ftime-poverty-is-making-indian-women-lose-more-money-than-ever%2F515811%2F%5C%22%3Etime%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDivya%20Pradeep%20teaches%20Economics%20at%20CHRIST%20(Deemed%20to%20be%20University)%2C%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694512848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fgruha-lakshmi-despite-flak-karnataka-cash-transfer-scheme-is-a-powerful-tool-to-empower-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Led%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20against%20welfare%20schemes%20involving%20the%20transfer%20of%20money%20or%20free%20goods.%20But%2C%20research%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20from%20across%20India%2C%20shows%20that%20cash%20transfers%20act%20as%20a%20viable%20redistributive%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20In%20Three%20Female%20Surgeons%20In%20UK%20Have%20Been%20Sexually%20Assaulted%3A%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFemale%20surgeons%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20raped%20by%20colleagues%2C%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20a%20new%20survey%20has%20revealed.%20The%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20British%20Journal%20of%20Surgery%20(BJS)%20and%20shared%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20examined%20sexual%20conduct%20in%20the%20UK%20surgical%20workforce%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20It%20found%20that%20almost%20one%20in%20three%20female%20surgeons%20working%20in%20the%20NHS%20(National%20Health%20Service)%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20colleagues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbjs%2Fadvance-article%2Fdoi%2F10.1093%2Fbjs%2Fznad242%2F7264733%3Fsearchresult%3D1%26login%3Dfalse%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20registered%20surgeons%20-%20men%20and%20women%20-%20were%20invited%20to%20take%20part%20completely%20anonymously%20and%201%2C434%20responded.%20It%20found%20that%2030%25%20of%20female%20surgeons%20who%20responded%20said%20they%20had%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%2029%25%20of%20women%20had%20experienced%20unwanted%20physical%20advances%20at%20work%2C%20over%2040%25%20had%20received%20uninvited%20comments%20about%20their%20body%20and%2038%25%20received%20sexual%20%26quot%3Bbanter%26quot%3B%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B90%25%20of%20women%2C%20and%2081%25%20of%20men%2C%20had%20witnessed%20some%20form%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-66775015%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20citing%20the%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20concluded%20that%20men%20and%20women%20surgeons%20are%20%26quot%3Bliving%20different%20realities%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSexual%20misconduct%20occurs%20frequently%20and%20appears%20to%20go%20unchecked%20in%20the%20surgical%20environment%20owing%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20a%20deeply%20hierarchical%20structure%20and%20a%20gender%20and%20power%20imbalance.%20The%20result%20is%20an%20unsafe%20working%20environment%20and%20an%20unsafe%20space%20for%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2023%2Fsep%2F12%2Ffemale-surgeons-nhs-sexually-assaulted-metoo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaken-hostage-in-kuwait-in-1990-uk-passengers-crew-to-sue-british-airways-4381776%5C%22%3ETaken%20Hostage%20In%20Kuwait%20In%201990%2C%20UK%20Passengers%2C%20Crew%20To%20Sue%20British%20Airways%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20found%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20faith%20in%20bodies%20such%20as%20NHS%20Trust%2C%20the%20General%20Medical%20Council%20and%20the%20Royal%20Colleges%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%20Only%2015.1%25%20of%20women%20regarded%20the%20GMC%20as%20adequate%20in%20their%20handling%20of%20sexual%20misconduct.%20Evaluations%20of%20National%20Health%20Service%20Trusts%20were%20comparatively%20low.%20Only%2015.8%25%20of%20women%20rated%20them%20as%20adequate%20and%2044.9%25%20of%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20major%20change%20in%20investigation%20processes%20so%20they%20become%20external%20and%20independent%2C%20and%20are%20trusted%20in%20order%20for%20healthcare%20to%20become%20a%20safer%20place%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Carrie%20Newlands%2C%20consultant%20surgeon%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20for%20staff%2C%20workplace%20harassment%20could%20be%20detrimental%20to%20their%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%2C%20with%20cases%20even%20leading%20to%20self-harm%20and%20victims%20contemplating%20suicide.%20The%20researchers%20called%20for%20action%20to%20improve%20the%20culture%20in%20the%20surgical%20workforce%20and%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20adequate%20mechanisms%20to%20deal%20with%20perpetrators%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694512740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fuf97do2_doctor-generic-unsplash_625x300_16_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fone-in-three-female-surgeons-in-uk-have-been-sexually-assaulted-reveals-survey-4382578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Female%20surgeons%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20raped%20by%20colleagues%2C%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20a%20new%20survey%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fone-in-three-female-surgeons-in-uk-have-been-sexually-assaulted-reveals-survey-4382578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fone-in-three-female-surgeons-in-uk-have-been-sexually-assaulted-reveals-survey-4382578%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fone-in-three-female