80%99%3A%20South%20Asian%20Diaspora%20on%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Hinduphobia%E2%80%99%20Petition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09191115%2Fimage-829.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20South%20Asian%20Dalit%20Adivasi%20Network%20(SADAN)%2C%20Canada%2C%20on%20September%2010%2C%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20petition%20e-4507%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20introduce%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESADAN%20says%20that%20it%20stands%20in%20solidarity%20with%20all%20racialised%20communities%20who%20face%20prejudice%20and%20discrimination.%20It%20acknowledges%20that%20people%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20origin%20do%20experience%20forms%20of%20racism.%20However%2C%20it%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20campaign%20for%20the%20Hinduphobia%20Bill%20is%20part%20of%20larger%20efforts%20to%3Cbr%3E%5Cnsuppress%20discussion%20about%20the%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20India%20and%20in%20Canada%20using%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20a%20shield.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20campaign%20to%20recognise%20Hinduphobia%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20dominant%20caste%20privileged%20South%20Asian%20diaspora%20who%20aim%20to%20obfuscate%20any%20discussion%20about%20the%20violence%20against%20Dalits%20(formerly%20untouchables)%2C%20Adivasis%20(Indigenous%20communities%20and%20tribes)%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%20in%20India.%20Claims%20of%20Hinduphobia%20have%20been%20used%20to%20persecute%2C%20hound%2C%20delegitimise%20and%20silence%20the%20fight%20against%20casteism%20and%20the%20oppression%20of%20minorities%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20caution%20you%20that%20supporting%20this%20petition%20will%20have%20a%20disastrous%20impact%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20caste-oppressed%20communities%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20in%20Canada%2C%20India%20and%20beyond%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20SADAN%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20requested%20all%20the%20elected%20representatives%20to%20oppose%20the%20petition%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20ensuring%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%2C%20in%20Canada%20and%20globally%2C%20remain%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20SADAN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Organization%20for%20Hindu%20Heritage%20Education%2C%20calling%20upon%20the%20House%20to%20recognise%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20term%20in%20the%20glossary%20of%20terms%20in%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Code.%20The%20term%20aims%20to%20recognise%20anti-Hindu%20prejudice%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20is%20defined%20as%20the%20denial%2C%20negation%2C%20prejudice%20or%20vilification%20against%20Hindus%2C%20Hinduism%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9CHinduness%E2%80%9D.%20The%20petition%20aims%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20address%20systemic%20and%20institutional%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09191115%2Fimage-829.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisastrous-impact-on-minorities-safety-south-asian-diaspora-on-canadas-hinduphobia-petition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Claims%20of%20Hinduphobia%20have%20been%20used%20to%20persecute%2C%20hound%2C%20delegitimise%20and%20silence%20the%20fight%20against%20casteism%20and%20the%20oppression%20of%20minorities%20in%20India%2C'%20said%20the%20South%20Asian%20Dalit%20Adivasi%20Network%2C%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisastrous-impact-on-minorities-safety-south-asian-diaspora-on-canadas-hinduphobia-petition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20To%20Sell%20Made-In-India%20iPhones%20On%20Launch%20Day%20For%20First%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20new%20iPhone%20model%20you%20buy%20on%20the%20launch%20day%20could%20be%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20Inc.%20plans%20to%20make%20the%20India-built%20iPhone%2015%20available%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country%20and%20some%20other%20regions%20on%20the%20global%20sales%20debut%20day%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20iPhone%2015s%20will%20come%20from%20China%2C%20that%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20latest%20generation%2C%20India-assembled%20device%20is%20available%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20sale%2C%20they%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20matter%20is%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20underscore%20India's%20growing%20production%20prowess%2C%20and%20reflect%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20Apple's%20previous%20strategy%20of%20selling%20mostly%20Chinese-made%20new%20devices%20to%20frenzied%20customers%20across%20the%20world.%20The%20new%20iPhone%2015%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20on%20sale%20in%20the%20days%20or%20weeks%20after%20its%20unveiling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECupertino%2C%20California-based%20Apple%20began%20iPhone%2015%20production%20at%20supplier%20Foxconn%20Technology%20Group's%20factory%20in%20southern%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20last%20month.%20That%20move%20was%20yet%20another%20effort%20by%20the%20US%20tech%20giant%20to%20further%20narrow%20the%20gap%20between%20its%20India%20operations%20and%20its%20main%20manufacturing%20bases%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlight%20delays%20with%20the%20India-built%20device%20could%20occur%20because%20of%20unforeseen%20logistics%20bottlenecks%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20Apple%20representatives%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20set%20to%20introduce%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%20updated%20watches%20and%20AirPods%20at%20a%20gala%20event%20at%20its%20US%20headquarters.%20Sales%20of%20new%20products%20begin%20typically%20around%2010%20days%20after%20the%20unveiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20iPhone%2014%2C%20Apple%20assembled%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20global%20output%20in%20India%2C%20which%20lagged%20behind%20China%20production%20by%20six%20to%20nine%20months.%20That%20delay%20was%20drastically%20reduced%20last%20year%20to%20just%20weeks%2C%20and%20Apple%20has%20increased%20the%20proportion%20of%20iPhones%20it%20assembles%20in%20India%20to%20reach%207%25%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20financial%20incentives%20to%20boost%20local%20manufacturing%20and%20Apple's%20strategy%20to%20look%20beyond%20China%20have%20helped%20India%20become%20increasingly%20important%20to%20the%20iPhone%20maker's%20diversification%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2015%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20update%20to%20the%20device%20in%20three%20years.%20It%20will%20include%20upgrades%20to%20the%20camera%20system%20across%20the%20range%2C%20and%20the%20Pro%20models%20will%20gain%20an%20improved%203-nanometer%20processor.%20The%20new%20lineup%20is%20critical%20to%20reviving%20flagging%20sales.%20Apple%20in%20August%20reported%20its%20third%20straight%20quarter%20of%20declining%20sales%2C%20weighed%20down%20by%20tepid%20consumer%20demand%20in%20key%20markets%20like%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Apple%20suppliers%20in%20India%20-%20Pegatron%20Corp.%20and%20a%20Wistron%20Corp.%20factory%20that%20is%20soon%20being%20acquired%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group%20-%20will%20also%20likely%20soon%20assemble%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20which%20opened%20its%20first%20I