oth-houses-to-bid-farewell-to-old-parliament-building%2Farticleshow%2F103519895.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eheadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CJoint%20sitting%20of%20both%20Houses%20to%20bid%20farewell%20to%20old%20Parliament%20building%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20question%20mark%20is%20normal%2C%20because%20few%20know%20what%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20special%20session%20is.%20The%20report%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CJust%20ahead%20of%20the%20five-day%20special%20session%2C%20there%20is%20considerable%20speculation%20over%20whether%20a%20joint%20meeting%20of%20the%20two%20Houses%20will%20be%20convened%20on%20September%2019%20in%20the%20iconic%20Central%20Hall%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20the%20existing%20Parliament%20building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20one%20need%20five%20days%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20a%20building%3F%20And%20why%20is%20there%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cconsiderable%20speculation%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20democracy%20when%20laws%20and%20changes%20should%20be%20discussed%20openly%20and%20transparently%3F%20On%20this%2C%20the%20report%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20enlightenment%20to%20readers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20special%20session%20was%20first%20announced%20on%20August%2031%2C%20there%20began%20a%20guessing%20game%20on%20why%20it%20was%20being%20called%20so%20shortly%20after%20one%20session%20had%20just%20ended%20on%20August%2011.%20The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20it%20was%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20country%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbharat-india-hindustan-history%5C%22%3EIndia%20to%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20days%20of%20media%20focus%20went%20into%20that.%20Ministers%20defended%20the%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20it%2C%20but%20were%20unable%20to%20confirm%20whether%20or%20not%20this%20change%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20what%20the%20session%20was%20for.%20Another%20guess%20was%20that%20it%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill.%20This%20was%20originally%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202008%2C%20but%20since%20then%20it%20has%20stalled%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20and%20demands%20of%20sub-reservations%20within%20this%20category%20for%20marginalised%20sections.%20If%20this%20is%20on%20the%20agenda%20and%20it%20goes%20through%2C%20it%20will%20set%20aside%20one-third%20of%20all%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20for%20women.%20This%20is%20a%20considerable%20reform%2C%20and%20if%20it%20is%20indeed%20this%20law%20that%20is%20being%20taken%20up%2C%20one%20hopes%20that%20it%20passes.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20guess%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20government%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20was%20calling%20the%20general%20election%20early.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20due%20in%20April-May%20next%20year%2C%20meaning%20in%20another%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20but%20they%20might%20be%20advanced%20just%20as%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20had%20done%20in%202004.%20This%20theory%20has%20not%20found%20many%20takers%2C%20but%20again%2C%20who%20knows%3F%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20gambit%20to%20call%20elections%20early%20did%20not%20succeed%20and%20the%20government%20fell%2C%20so%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20caution%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20fervent%20speculation%20was%20around%20something%20called%20%E2%80%9Cone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20system%20whereby%20all%20states%20and%20the%20Centre%20will%20go%20into%20elections%20every%20five%20years%20together%20and%20citizens%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Will%20corporation%20elections%20also%20be%20included%3F%20One%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20byelections%3F%20And%20how%20will%20the%20EVMs%20be%20set%20up%20for%20multiple%20elections%3F%20One%20does%20not%20know%20that%20either%2C%20but%20perhaps%20wiser%20minds%20have%20already%20sorted%20all%20such%20things%20out.%20A%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20under%20a%20former%20President%20to%20look%20into%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20how%20this%20committee%20will%20meet%20and%20give%20its%20findings%20all%20in%20time%20for%20the%20special%20session%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20more%20story%20floated%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20session%20was%20about%20a%20commission%20set%20up%20in%202017%20to%20look%20at%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20so%20that%20reservations%20could%20be%20made%20more%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20form%20of%20government%20carries%20with%20it%20something%20called%20collective%20responsibility%2C%20meaning%20that%20decisions%20are%20jointly%20owned.%20But%20here%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20is%20as%20much%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20decisions%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20are.%20Two%20instances%20from%20the%20past%20will%20suffice%20to%20demonstrate%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20a%20report%20from%20November%2010%2C%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdon-t-bring-your-phones-modi-s-cabinet-meet-that-took-everyone-by-surprise%2Fstory-YEbaMM3lr3McikFnnSZTmL.html%5C%22%3Eheadlined%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20bring%20your%20phones%3A%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Cabinet%20meet%20that%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise.%E2%80%9D%20The%20report%20said%20Union%20ministers%20found%20out%20about%20demonetisation%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%20meaning%20that%20it%20was%20neither%20discussed%20nor%20debated.%20Another%20instance%20is%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20filing%20of%20over%20240%20Right%20to%20Information%20queries%20with%20the%20government%20about%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%202020.%20It%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20departments%20of%20health%2C%20finance%2C%20disaster%20management%20and%20the%20rest%20about%20what%20they%20knew%20regarding%20the%20lockdown%20and%20how%20they%20prepared.%20The%20answer%20was%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20and%20did%20not%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20government%2C%20where%20secrets%20and%20major%20decisions%20are%20kept%20from%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20continuing%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20speculation%20around%20this%20special%20session.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20Question%20Hour%20either%20in%20this%20session%2C%20and%20while%20this%20is%20expected%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary.%20Even%20questions%20asked%20are%20not%20answered%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20so%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20stopping%20them%20from%20being%20asked%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20sent%20a%20list%20of%20things%20they%20would%20like%20discussed%20in%20the%20session.%20These%20include%20inflation%2C%20joblessness%2C%20MSP%20for%20farmers%2C%20the%20continuing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Adani%20scandal%2C%20communal%20tensions%20across%20India%2C%20the%20Chinese%20actions%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20(or%20any%20census%2C%20given%20that%20the%20primary%20one%20has%20been%20inexplicably%20delayed)%2C%20the%20strains%20on%20federalism%20and%20impact%20of%20natural%20disasters%20and%20climate%20change.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%2C%20assuming%20these%20are%20not%20already%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20they%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20even%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%20has%20such%20little%20say%20in%20what%20should%20be%20discussed%20and%20passed%2C%20why%20should%20the%20Opposition%20be%20listened%20to%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-issues-will-the-5-day-special-session-take-up-no-one-knows-not-even-the-cabinet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20announces%20%2410%20bln%20local%20bond%20swap%20deal%20ahead%20of%20IMF%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694510054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103603534%2Cimgsize-23198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-announces-10-bln-local-bond-swap-deal-ahead-of-imf-visit%2Farticleshow%2F103603432.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103603432.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESri%20Lanka%20has%20accepted%20offers%20to%20exchange%20%2410%20billion%20worth%20of%20defaulted%20local%20debt%20for%20new%20bonds%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20debt%20restructuring%20requirements.%20The%20exchange%2C%20which%20includes%203.2%20trillion%20rupees%20of%20eligible%20bonds%2C%20will%20help%20reduce%20the%20country's%20Gross%20Financing%20Needs%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20exchange%20will%20also%20contribute%20to%20achieving%20Sri%20Lanka's%20debt%20reduction%20targets%20set%20under%20the%20IMF%20program.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-announces-10-bln-local-bond-swap-deal-ahead-of-imf-visit%2Farticleshow%2F103603432.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-announces-10-bln-local-bond-swap-deal-ahead-of-imf-visit%2Famp_articleshow%2F103603432.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-announces-10-bln-local-bond-swap-deal-ahead-of-imf-visit%2Famp_articleshow%2F103603432.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Government%20Headed%20for%20a%20Dal-Roti%20Mess%20as%20Traders%20Make%20a%20Killing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12124516%2Fangshu-purkait-UwdHrmoE0fU-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELentils%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20have%20a%20peculiar%20relationship.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20government%20faced%20hyperinflation%20in%20dal%20prices%2C%20and%20now%2C%20over%20nine%20years%20later%2C%20India%20is%20once%20again%20grappling%20with%20imminent%20dal%20and%20food%20price%20inflation%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDal%20prices%20have%20already%20begun%20to%20rise%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20prompting%20hoarders%20and%20big%20traders%20to%20stockpile%20dals%20in%20their%20warehouses.%20The%20government%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202015%20dal%20crisis%2C%20has%20been%20carefully%20managing%20the%20food%20economy%20through%20export%20and%20import%20bans%20and%20custom%20duties.%20But%20the%20recent%20government%20order%20concerning%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20chana%20dals%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20wrote%20to%20all%20state%20chief%20secretaries%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20ensure%20that%20any%20available%20stocks%20of%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20urad%20dal%20with%20stockists%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20are%20declared%20on%20the%20government%20portal.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20all-India%20average%20price%20of%20tur%2Farhar%20dal%20has%20surged%2025%25%20to%20Rs%20128.66%20per%20kg%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20open%20up%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20there%20may%20be%20issues%20with%20importers%20as%20well.%20The%20government%20issued%20another%20clarification%2C%20requiring%20importers%20of%20pulses%20to%20compulsorily%20declare%20their%20available%20stocks.%20This%20step%20became%20necessary%20as%20several%20importers%20had%20been%20holding%20dal%20stocks%20after%20benefiting%20from%20relaxed%20import%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20government%20reduced%20import%20duties%20on%20dal%2C%20flooding%20the%20markets.%20But%20neither%20consumers%20nor%20farmers%20have%20benefited%20from%20this%20policy%20because%20importers%2C%20foreign%20traders%20and%20large%20stockholders%20have%20once%20again%20reaped%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20the%20imports%2C%20which%20is%20in%20their%20godowns.%20While%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20curb%20dal%20price%20inflation.%20In%20fact%2C%20some%20measures%20may%20inadvertently%20favour%20these%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20the%20case%3F%20Firstly%2C%20the%20government%20allowed%20the%20cartel%20responsible%20for%20dal%20price%20manipulation%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20to%20go%20unpunished.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20attempted%20to%20dismantle%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%20as%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20laws.%20A%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0investigation%20initiated%20by%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20was%20closed%20for%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20two%20government%20departments%20could%20study%20the%20same%20problem%20and%20arrive%20at%20different%20conclusions.%20While%20the%20IT%20department%20found%20evidence%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccartelization%E2%80%9D%20and%20conducted%20an%20investigation%2C%20the%20CCI%20did%20not%20find%20sufficient%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELentils%20are%20a%20major%20protein%20source%20for%20most%20Indians%2C%20yet%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20hoarders%20or%20foreign%20corporations%20that%20openly%20profited%20from%20price%20manipulation%20in%202015.%20The%20same%20people%20are%20probably%20exploiting%20loopholes%20to%20profit%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20hunger%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20discuss%20dal%20import%20custom%20duties%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20G20.%20Lowering%20customs%20duties%20on%20US-origin%20lentils%20like%20chickpeas%20is%20a%20way%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1694575916243000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0TafU7XM6rX63qGhePUAhz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappease%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20US%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20exporters%20of%20lentils%20to%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20progressively%20reduced%20duties%20on%20US-origin%20lentils%20from%2030%25%20to%2020%25%2C%20and%20now%20to%20none.%20This%20move%20serves%20a%20dual%20purpose%3A%20it%20creates%20demand%20for%20cheap%20exports%20due%20to%20artificial%20scarcity%2C%20allows%20India%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ties%20with%20Biden%20and%20enables%20Modi%20to%20acquire%20US%20dal%20along%20with%20second-grade%20weapons%20systems.%20This%20pleases%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20electorate%2C%20benefits%20Modi%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa078b3f3-a773-4a6c-86e4-115800762a19%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1694575916243000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0TafU7XM6rX63qGhePUAhz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexempts%20corporations%20selling%20dal%20from%20custom%20duties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20domestic%20producers%20and%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%98killing%E2%80%99%20may%20sound%20harsh%2C%20but%20it%20accurately%20describes%20the%20plight%20of%20Indian%20farmers%20who%20have%20repeatedly%20appealed%20to%20the%20government%20for%20a%20lucrative%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20on%20lentils.%20Within%20three%20years%2C%20this%20could%20help%20safeguard%20foreign%20reserves%20and%20make%20India%20sovereign%20in%20this%20category.%20Even%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Sangh%20has%20repeatedly%20written%20to%20the%20government%20regarding%20oilseeds%20and%20lentils.%20However%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20government%20is%20prioritising%20American%20farmers.%20Since%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20first%20term%2C%20lentil%20imports%20have%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20this%20trend%20is%20likely%20to%20persist%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20BJP%20or%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%2C%20as%20both%20parties%20have%20similar%20agricultural%20import%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20inflation%20already%20at%20a%20peak%2C%20food%20security%20will%20become%20an%20even%20more%20pressing%20concern%20than%20anticipated.%20After%20enduring%20vegetable%20price%20inflation%2C%20consumers%20and%20farmers%20are%20growing%20frustrated.%20If%20the%20government%20mishandles%20the%20lentil%20supply%20and%20fails%20to%20control%20inflation%2C%20India%20will%20not%20remain%20silent%2C%20as%20this%20issue%20directly%20impacts%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edal-roti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20basic%20staple%20of%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20is%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks%E2%80%99.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694509244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12124516%2Fangshu-purkait-UwdHrmoE0fU-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-government-headed-for-a-dal-roti-mess-as-traders-make-a-killing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202015%20dal%20crisis%2C%20has%20been%20carefully%20managing%20the%20food%20economy%20through%20export%20and%20import%20bans%20and%20custom%20duties.%20But%20a%20recent%20government%20order%20concerning%20masoor%2C%20tur%20and%20chana%20dals%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-government-headed-for-a-dal-roti-mess-as-traders-make-a-killing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maria%20Ressa%3A%20Philippines%20Nobel%20laureate%20acquitted%20in%20court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694508840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF952%2Fproduction%2F_131062836_0263d18dcc1a23c39739f61da14707ab1ba72615.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2F66782826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Renowned%20Filipina%20journa