%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconcealing%E2%80%9D%20an%20alert%20it%20received%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20in%20January%202014%20about%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpetitioner-in-sc-accuses-sebi-of-concealing-2014-dri-alert-on-adani%2Farticle67295917.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Anamika%20Jaiswal%2C%20represented%20by%20advocates%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20and%20Cheryl%20D%E2%80%99Souza%2C%20alleged%20that%20SEBI%20had%20%E2%80%9Cconcealed%20a%20January%202014%20DRI%20alert%20about%20Adani%20having%20siphoned%20off%20money%20and%20invested%20them%20in%20Adani%20listed%20companies%20through%20entities%20based%20in%20Dubai%20and%20Mauritius%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20claimed%20the%20DRI%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20then%20SEBI%20chairperson%2C%20U.K.%20Sinha%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%202014%2C%20alerting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20may%20be%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20companies%20using%20the%20money%20siphoned%20off%20through%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20power%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20DRI%20had%20sent%20a%20CD%2C%20containing%20evidence%20of%20siphoning%20of%20Rs%202%2C323%20crore%20and%20notes%20on%20the%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20anti-smuggling%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-hhE_MfhZgY%5C%22%3Elatest%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20And%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20says%2C%20citing%20documents%2C%20which%20it%20also%20shared%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Sinha%2C%20the%20then%20SEBI%20head%2C%20currently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fndtv-appoints-former-sebi-chairman-uk-sinha-as-non-executive-chairman-16279441.htm%5C%22%3Eserves%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20non-executive%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20SEBI%20has%20not%20disclosed%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20said%20letter%20(DRI%20letter)%20and%20evidence%20from%20the%20DRI%20till%20date%20before%20this%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20citing%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20previous%20statements%20to%20the%20top%20court%20that%20it%20started%20the%20investigation%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20only%20in%20June-July%202020%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20alleged%20that%20this%20was%20suppression%20of%20facts%20and%20providing%20false%20information%20which%20amounts%20to%20perjury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%202014%20DRI%20letter%2C%20the%20affidavit%20brought%20attention%20to%20numerous%20other%20key%20aspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConflict%20of%20interest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbreaking-sebi-concealed-2014-dri-alert-about-adani-group-manipulations-has-conflict-of-interest-petitioner-tells-supreme-court-237522%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20affidavit%20pointed%20out%20that%20Cyril%20Shroff%2C%20managing%20partner%2C%20Cyril%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%2C%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20committee%20on%20corporate%20governance%2C%20which%20looks%20at%20offences%20such%20as%20insider%20trading.%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20is%20married%20to%20Karan%20Adani%2C%20son%20of%20Gautam%20Adani.%20Hence%2C%20the%20relation%20causes%20the%20conflict%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20out%20of%2024%20SEBI%20investigation%20reports%20are%20on%20insider%20trading%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20companies%2C%20said%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmendments%20of%20the%20FPI%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulations%20initially%20mandated%20that%20designated%20depository%20participants%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20had%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%20did%20not%20maintain%20opaque%20structures.%20However%2C%20in%202018%2C%20SEBI%20revised%20this%20requirement%20by%20redefining%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98ultimate%20beneficial%20owners%E2%80%99%20to%20align%20with%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98beneficial%20owner%E2%80%99%20as%20defined%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20July%2011%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20explain%20why%20the%20law%20was%20tweaked%20in%202018%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20change%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsc-asks-sebi-why-changes-were-made-to-law-that-limited-its-ability-to-probe-opacity-in-fpi-ownership%5C%22%3Eis%20absolutely%20fatal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20current%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20SEBI%20repealed%20the%202014%20provisions%20on%20%E2%80%9Copaque%20structures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F6-out-of-8-offshore-funds-used-for-share-purchases-in-adani-firms-shut-down-amid-allegations%5C%22%3E6%20Out%20of%208%20Offshore%20Funds%20Used%20for%20Share%20Purchases%20in%20Adani%20Firms%20Shut%20Down%20Amid%20Probe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20the%20changes%20significant%3F%20Because%20the%20Supreme%20Court-led%20expert%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20if%20there%20was%20violation%20of%20the%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%2C%20or%20free%20float%2C%20norms%20by%20the%20Adani%20group.%20Hindenburg%20Research%20alleged%20that%20overseas%20entities%20and%20shell%20companies%20that%20were%20tied%20to%20Adani%20group%20%E2%80%9Csurreptitiously%E2%80%9D%20owned%20stock%20in%20its%20listed%20firms.%20This%20indicated%20a%20violation%20of%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20free%20float%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublicly%20traded%20companies%20are%20required%20to%20have%20at%20least%2025%25%20of%20their%20shares%20held%20by%20non-promoters%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20retail%20investors%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20FPIs%2C%20and%20insurance%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20to%20stay%20listed%20on%20exchanges.%20These%20shares%20are%20called%20public%20float%20or%20free%20float%20or%20public%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20listed%20is%20critical%20as%20it%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20money%20from%20the%20market.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20these%20rules%20are%20not%20met%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-vinod-adani-free-float-rules%5C%22%3Eimplications%20on%20these%20companies%E2%80%99%20public%20listing%20status.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefinition%20of%20related%20party%20amended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20SEBI%20Listing%20Obligations%20and%20Disclosure%20Requirement%20(LODR)%2C%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98related%20party%E2%80%99%20was%20originally%20defined%20to%20align%20with%20the%20definition%20provided%20in%20Section%202(76)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20However%2C%20in%202018%2C%20SEBI%20made%20an%20amendment%20to%20this%20definition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20amendment%20introduced%20a%20separate%20provision%20that%20enabled%20a%20member%20or%20entity%20of%20the%20promoter%20group%20of%20a%20listed%20company%20as%20a%20related%20party%20only%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20that%20person%20was%20at%20least%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694502918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-concealed-dri-letter-on-stock-market-manipulation-by-adani-group-in-2014-petitioner-to-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20the%202014%20DRI%20letter%2C%20the%20affidavit%20brought%20attention%20to%20numerous%20other%20key%20issues%20such%20as%20amendments%20to%20FPI%20regulations%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator%20in%202018%20and%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Case%20for%20Not%20Celebrating%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20on%20September%205%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11184203%2FCopy-of-Lead-image-size-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETeachers%E2%80%99%20Day%20in%20India%2C%20celebrated%20on%20September%205%2C%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20day%20to%20honour%20educators%20and%20their%20contributions%20to%20society.%20The%20date%20coincides%20with%20the%20birthday%20of%20Dr.%20Sarvepalli%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20a%20philosopher%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20president.%20However%2C%20revelations%20about%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20plagiarism%20and%20controversial%20views%20on%20women%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20appropriateness%20of%20celebrating%20his%20birthday%20as%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20259px)%2085vw%2C%20259px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FDr.Sarvepalli_Radhakrishnan-259x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22259%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FDr.Sarvepalli_Radhakrishnan-259x300.jpg%20259w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FDr.Sarvepalli_Radhakrishnan.jpg%20459w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-4366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESarvepalli%20Radhakrishnan.%20Photo%20Division%2C%20GOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%20was%20grounded%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvaita%20Vedanta%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(a%20school%20of%20Hindu%20philosophy)%2C%20reinterpreting%20this%20tradition%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiep.utm.edu%2Fradhakri%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econtemporary%20understanding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20defended%20Hinduism%20against%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cuninformed%20Western%20criticism%E2%80%9D%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20contemporary%20Hindu%20identity.%3Cspan%3E%20He%20was%20influential%20in%20shaping%20the%20understanding%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20earned%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20bridge-builder%20between%20India%20and%20the%20West%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20later%20years%2C%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20Eastern%20philosophy%20also%20came%20under%20scrutiny.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fradhakrishnan-hinduism-rss-gita-veda-upanishad%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20argue%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20oversimplified%20and%20misrepresented%20complex%20Eastern%20philosophical%20concepts%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20make%20them%20more%20palatable%20to%20Western%20audiences.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20may%20have%20compromised%20the%20authenticity%20and%20depth%20of%20these%20philosophical%20traditions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%201929%2C%20Jadunath%20Sinha%2C%20a%20relatively%20unknown%20lecturer%20of%20philosophy%20at%20Meerut%20College%2C%20accused%20Radhakrishnan%20of%20extensive%20plagiarism.%20Sinha%20claimed%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fdr-sarvepalli-radhakrishnan-the-teacher-who-plagiarised-his-student-s-thesis%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERadhakrishnan%20had%20plagiarised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20first%20two%20parts%20of%20his%20thesis%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Psychology%20of%20Perception%2C%20Vol%20I%20%26amp%3B%20Vol%20II%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20were%20submitted%20to%20Calcutta%20University%20for%20the%20Premchand%20Roychand%20Studentship%20in%201922.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20allegations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fdr-sarvepalli-radhakrishnan-the-teacher-who-plagiarised-his-student-s-thesis%2F%5C%22%3Edocumented%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Utpal%20Aich%2C%20retired%20Indian%20diplomat%20and%20independent%20researcher%2C%20pertained%20to%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Philosophy%20Vol.%20II%2C%E2%80%99%20published%20in%201927%2C%20which%20allegedly%20incorporated%20stolen%20paragraphs%20from%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20thesis.%20Radhakrishnan%20had%20published%20another%20book%20titled%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Vedanta%20according%20to%20Sankara%20and%20Ramanuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201928%2C%20which%20was%20actually%20a%20reprint%20of%20Chapters%208%20and%209%20of%20his%20book%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20Philosophy%20Vol.%20II.%E2%80%9D%20That%20book%20also%20had%20extensive%20pirated%20paragraphs%20from%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20Premchand%20Roychand%20Studentship%20thesis.%20Luckily%20for%20Sinha%2C%20he%20had%20published%20extracts%20from%20those%20two%20parts%20of%20his%20Premchand%20Roychand%20Studentship%20thesis%20in%20the%20Meerut%20College%20Magazines%20of%201924%20and%201926.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20282px)%2085vw%2C%20282px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11181739%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-6.17.17-PM-204x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22282%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11181739%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-6.17.17-PM-204x300.png%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11181739%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-6.17.17-PM-697x1024.png%20697w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11181739%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-6.17.17-PM.png%20817w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22415%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESarvepalli%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20Indian%20Philosophy%20(1923).%20Photo%3A%20Public%20domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20writing%20letters%20about%20this%20matter%2C%20which%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fdr-sarvepalli-radhakrishnan-the-teacher-who-plagiarised-his-student-s-thesis%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublished%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EModern%20Review%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20defamation%20from%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20Sinha%20sued%20him%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20for%20infringement%20of%20copyrights%20of%20his%20original%20literary%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20Sinha%20to%20settle%20the%20case%20out%20of%20court.%20All%20the%20senior%20professors%20who%20sympathised%20with%20Sinha%20and%20were%20convinced%20of%20the%20plagiarism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fdr-sarvepalli-radhakrishnan-the-teacher-who-plagiarised-his-student-s-thesis%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20refused%20to%20stand%20as%20a%20witness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20him%20in%20the%20court.%20Sinha%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20fight%20a%20prolonged%20legal%20battle%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Radhakrishnan%20had%20both%20financial%20and%20social%20capital%20to%20manipulate%2C%20manage%20and%20obtain%20the%20help%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20especially%20that%20of%20Shyamaprasad%20Mukherjee%2C%20son%20of%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukheriee.%20It%20was%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukheriee%2C%20the%20then%20vice%20chancellor%20of%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20who%20had%20brought%20Radhakrishnan%20from%20Bangalore%20to%20Calcutta%20University%20for%20the%20prestigious%20post%20of%20King%20George%20V%20Professorship%20on%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201000%20per%20month.%20His%20son%2C%20Shyamaprasad%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Dr.%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20therefore%2C%20wanted%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20book%20on%20Radhakirishnan%E2%80%99s%20plagiarism%2C%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Reported%20case%20of%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20Literary%20Piracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Barin%20De%2C%20based%20on%20the%20documents%20submitted%20by%20Sinha%20in%20the%20court%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Ftitle%2Freported-case-of-radhakrishnans-literary-piracy%2Foclc%2F56322949%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econveniently%20vanished%20from%20the%20libraries%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Aich.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20plagiarism%20allegations%20against%20Radhakrishnan%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20his%20legacy%20as%20an%20educator%20and%20philosopher.%20Such%20accusations%20not%20only%20question%20the%20integrity%20of%20a%20celebrated%20figure%20but%20also%20challenge%20the%20principles%20of%20academic%20honesty%20and%20authenticity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAside%20from%20the%20plagiarism%20allegations%2C%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20women%20have%20also%20raised%20eyebrows.%20He%20believed%20that%20the%20role%20of%20women%20was%20best%20fulfilled%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20marriage%20and%20motherhood.%20Notably%2C%20Radhakrishnan%20arranged%20the%20marriages%20of%20his%20daughters%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20were%20married%20off%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20Radhakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20biography%20written%20by%20his%20son%20Sarvepalli%20Gopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20juxtaposition%20of%20his%20traditional%20views%20on%20women%20with%20his%20celebrated%20role%20as%20an%20educator%2C%20then%2C%20seem%20hypocritical.%20Celebrating%20a%20figure%20who%20held%20such%20views%20as%20the%20symbol%20of%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20may%20send%20the%20wrong%20message%20about%20the%20values%20that%20educators%20should%20uphold%2C%20including%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnother%20contender%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESavitribai%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20educating%20girls%2C%20especially%20girls%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%20was%20revolutionary%20not%20only%20for%20her%20time%20but%20even%20today.%20Her%20unwavering%20dedication%20to%20breaking%20the%20barriers%20of%20caste%20and%20gender%2C%20along%20with%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20provide%20education%20to%20those%20who%20were%20denied%20it%2C%20make%20her%20a%20true%20icon%20of%20education%20and%20social%20reform.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20important%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20Phule%20existed%20almost%20a%20century%20before%20Radhakrishnan%20and%20her%20ideas%20were%20centuries%20ahead%20of%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FSavitribai_Phule1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20portrait%20of%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22201%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-62063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20portrait%20of%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhule%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20contributions%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20female%20teacher%20and%20her%20relentless%20efforts%20in%20fighting%20caste-based%20discrimination%20make%20her%20an%20ideal%20choice%20to%20honour%20on%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day.%20She%20embodies%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20education%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20for%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20day%20to%20be%20celebrated%20on%20January%203%20i.e.%20Savitribai%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20instead%20of%20on%20September%205%2C%20in%20my%20humble%20opinion%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20to%20be%20made.%20A%20better%20birthday%20to%20commemorate%20and%20honour%20the%20true%20spirit%20and%20significance%20of%20a%20teacher%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20on%20the%20subcontinent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhule%20is%20considered%20the%20pioneer%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20feminist%20movement%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20education%20in%20India.%20She%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Jyotiba%20Phule%2C%20started%20the%20first%20modern%20day%20school%20for%20girls%20in%201848%20in%20Pune%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20time%20when%20girls%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20school%2C%20in%20Bhide%20Wada%2C%20which%20has%20so%20far%20existed%20in%20shambles%2C%20is%20only%20now%2C%20in%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fbhide-wada-to-be-national-monument-foundation-stone-in-2-months-maharashtra-cm-eknath-shinde%2Farticleshow%2F96722407.cms%5C%22%3Ebeing%20considered%20to%20be%20deemed%20as%20a%20heritage%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20redeveloped%20as%20a%20national%20monument.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20husband-wife%20duo%20opened%2018%20schools%20for%20children%20of%20different%20castes%20and%20established%20two%20educational%20trusts%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Native%20Female%20School%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20the%20Society%20for%20Promoting%20the%20Education%20of%20Mahars%2C%20Mangs%20and%20others.%20They%20also%20opened%20a%20care%20center%20called%20Balhatya%20Pratibandhak%20Griha%20for%20children%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20rape%2C%20sati%20and%20those%20who%20escaped%20female%20infanticide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESavitribai%20was%20the%20first%20woman%20in%20modern%20India%20to%20challenge%20the%20work%20prescribed%20for%20Hindu%20women%20by%20the%20scriptures%20n%2C%20social%20system%20and%20tradition%20for%20Shudra-Ati%20Shudras.%20She%20fought%20all%20her%20life%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20Shudra-Ati%20Shudras%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Phules%20stood%20as%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20Brahmanism%20and%20the%20road%20to%20ending%20their%20monopoly%20was%20paved%20with%20difficulty.%20The%20privileged%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20Brahmin%20class%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%20harassed%20the%20Phules%20because%20they%20belonged%20to%20the%20oppressed%20Mali%20caste.%20On%20her%20way%20to%20school%2C%20Savitribai%20was%20abused%20and%20had%20dung%20thrown%20at%20her.%20She%20simply%20changed%20into%20a%20spare%20saree%20she%20always%20carried%20with%20her%20and%20continued%20on%20her%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited.jpeg%20796w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FPhule-edited-300x148.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-23748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBusts%20of%20Mahatma%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20and%20Savitribai%20Phule.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20eventually%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagranjosh.com%2Fgeneral-knowledge%2Famp%2Fsavitribai-phule-biography-husband-children-work-for-girls-education-schools-awards-death-1641193310-1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eforced%20to%20leave%20Jyotiba%E2%80%99s%20father%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%201849%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20committing%20the%20sin%20of%20studying%20against%20Manusmriti%20and%20its%20Brahmanical%20texts.%20Given%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20over%20all%20resources%20in%20this%20country%2C%20especially%20education%20and%20the%20access%20it%20can%20provide%2C%20one%20must%20really%20sit%20and%20question%20why%20we%20think%20%E2%80%98Teacher%E2%80%99s%20day%E2%80%99%20and%20its%20celebration%20should%20be%20one%20that%20commemorates%20Brahmanism%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20inhuman%20exclusionary%20spirit%20that%20to%20this%20day%20marginalises%20such%20a%20vast%20population%20of%20this%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brahminical%20idea%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98teacher%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98guru%E2%80%99%2C%20that%20glorifies%20the%20ideas%20of%20authority%20and%20respect%20over%20the%20well%20being%20and%20democratisation%20of%20knowledge%2C%20that%20upholds%20the%20varna%20system%20and%20assigns%20occupations%20by%20birth%20and%20justifies%20who%20is%20worthy%20of%20knowledge%20and%20who%20is%20not%20is%20simply%20a%20heartless%20and%20cruel%20system%20of%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%5C%22%3Ekillings%20by%20suicide%20of%20students%20from%20SC%2FST%20backgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20premiere%20institutes%20is%20rampant%20because%20of%20the%20very%20Brahmanical%20nature%20of%20education%20in%20this%20country%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20and%20emulate%20Savitribai%20and%20what%20she%20fought%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%5C%22%3ETwo%20Dalit%20Students%E2%80%99%20Suicides%20in%20Two%20Months%20Highlight%20%E2%80%98Institutionalised%20Discrimination%E2%80%99%20at%20IITs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETeacher%E2%80%99s%20day%20should%20be%20about%20teachers%20who%20go%20against%20the%20grain%2C%20who%20fight%20injustice%20everyday%2C%20who%20crush%20hierarchies%2C%20who%20make%20education%20the%20tool%20of%20liberation%20that%20it%20can%20be%20and%20not%20about%20teachers%20who%20are%20plagiarists%2C%20who%20steal%20from%20their%20own%20students%20and%20further%20regressive%20views.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20a%20tradition%20in%20this%20country%2C%20to%20glorify%20Brahmin-Baniya%20men%2C%20to%20shower%20them%20with%20laurels%20and%20to%20celebrate%20them%20to%20no%20end%2C%20to%20forgive%20and%20justify%20their%20misdoings%20and%20misgivings%20as%20mere%20products%20of%20their%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20for%20people%20to%20really%20question%20the%20oppressive%20systems%20of%20this%20country%20that%20we%20live%20under%2C%20to%20ask%20what%20true%20education%20is%2C%20to%20differentiate%20between%20an%20education%20that%20empowers%20and%20an%20education%20that%20teaches%20you%20to%20bow%20down%20to%20authority.%20And%20it%20is%20certainly%20time%20to%20honour%20the%20eternal%20legacy%20of%20Phule%20%E2%80%93%20an%20educator%20and%20social%20reformer%20par%20excellence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPriyanka%20Paul%20is%20an%20illustrator%20and%20writer%20based%20in%20Mumbai.%20Their%20work%20revolves%20around%20the%20themes%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20self%20exploration%20and%20understanding%20marginalisation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694502007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11184203%2FCopy-of-Lead-image-size-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-case-for-not-celebrating-teachers-day-on-september-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plagiarism%20allegations%20against%20Radhakrishnan%20have%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20his%20legacy%20as%20an%20educator%20and%20philosopher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-case-for-not-celebrating-teachers-day-on-september-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kashmiris%20Made%20to%20Suffer%20for%20Applause%20from%20Abroad'%3A%20Fears%20Over%20Govt's%20Apple%20Import%20Tariff%20Slash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12115853%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20gaining%20momentum%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20waive%20off%2020%25%20tariff%20on%20imported%20apples%20is%20turning%20into%20a%20fresh%20headache%20for%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20urged%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janta%20Party-led%20Union%20government%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20decision%20while%20local%20stakeholders%20are%20anguished%20that%20the%20waiver%20will%20negatively%20impact%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20industry%2C%20which%20employs%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20people%20directly%20and%20indirectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%2C%20which%20has%20chopped%20off%20extra%2020%25%20from%20the%2070%25%20tariff%20imposed%20since%202019%20by%20New%20Delhi%20on%20the%20premium%20Washington%20apples%2C%20was%20announced%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20September%205%20when%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20reportedly%20released%20a%20notification%20ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20his%20US%20counterpart%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G-20%20Summit%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20announced%20the%20tax%20waiver%20on%20several%20US%20products%20such%20as%20walnuts%2C%20lentils%2C%20chickpeas%20and%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fg20-farmers-agriculture-bio-fuel-india-us%5C%22%3EThe%20G20%20Has%20Summarily%20Failed%20to%20Address%20Agrarian%20Distress%20in%20its%20Member%20Countries%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kashmir-based%20traders%20and%20growers%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Washington%20apples%20with%20a%20tax%20waiver%20into%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20set%20to%20pick%20up%20will%20lead%20to%20pricing%20fluctuations%20which%20will%20hit%20the%20local%20industry%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Kashmiris%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20foreign%20countries%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh%20inflation%20has%20already%20led%20to%20a%20shoot%20up%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20apple%20production%20while%20the%20yield%20has%20also%20fallen%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20tax%20waiver%20%5Bon%20imported%20US%20apples%5D%20will%20hit%20not%20just%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%20but%20also%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand.%20The%20government%20should%20reconsider%20the%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bashir%20Ahmad%20Bashir%2C%20president%20of%20the%20All%20Valley%20Fruit%20Growers%20and%20Dealers%20Association%20(AVFGDA)%2C%20the%20leading%20association%20of%20apple%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20function%20here%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20called%20for%20a%20rollback%20of%20the%20waiver%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Creflects%20the%20disconnect%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20imported%20apples%2C%20walnuts%20or%20almonds%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20government%20is%20increasing%20hardships%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20order%20to%20please%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries.%20Kashmiris%20are%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20the%20foreign%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20import%20tariff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmir%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20apple%20basket%2C%20producing%20around%2021%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20fruit%20last%20year%20(or%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20apples%20produced%20in%20India)%20which%20generates%20a%20revenue%20of%20between%20Rs%2010%2C000-Rs%2014%2C000%20crore%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20horticulture%20sector%20contributes%20around%20eight%20to%2010%25%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20were%20caught%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20when%2C%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Washington%20raised%20tariffs%20by%2010-25%25%20on%20specific%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20items%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20concerns.%20India%20followed%20suit%20by%20increasing%20tariffs%20on%20several%20US%20products%2C%20including%20Washington%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20extra%20tariff%20drastically%20reduced%20India%E2%80%99s%20apple%20imports%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20From%20US%20%24145.2%20million%20in%202018-19%20when%20the%20country%20imported%20US%20%24305.71%20million%20worth%20of%20apples%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data%2C%20the%20apple%20imports%20dropped%20to%20only%20US%20%245.27%20million%20in%202022-23%20when%20the%20total%20apple%20imports%20were%20at%20US%20%24295.94%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20Turkey%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20leading%20apple%20supplier%20for%20India%2C%20making%20up%20for%20more%20than%2084%25%20of%20total%20apple%20imports%20followed%20by%20Italy%2C%20Chile%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20harvest%20season%20picking%20up%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20premium%20quality%20Washington%20apples%20in%20the%20market%2C%20which%20are%20wax-polished%20to%20increase%20their%20shelf%20life%2C%20has%20dampened%20the%20spirits%20of%20local%20growers%20and%20traders%2C%20who%20were%20hoping%20to%20capitalise%20on%20low%20domestic%20production%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20suffered%20between%2040-50%25%20loss%20of%20apple%20produce%20due%20to%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20hailstorms%20and%20flood%20which%20led%20to%20spread%20of%20diseases%20such%20as%20scab%20and%20powdery%20mildew%20in%20apple%20trees%20and%20immature%20fruit%20droppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Pexels%2Frohitsinghprashar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20price%20difference%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20traders%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Delicious%20variety%2C%20which%20makes%2070-80%25%20of%20total%20apples%20produced%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%2075%20per%20kilogram%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20last%20year.%20One%20box%20of%20Kashmiri%20Red%20Delicious%20apples%2C%20which%20contains%20around%2020%20kilograms%20of%20fruit%2C%20fetches%20Rs%201%2C200-1%2C500%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fruit%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20a%20kilo%20of%20the%20imported%20US%20apples%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%20120%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20of%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20according%20to%20a%20trader.%20A%2032-kg%20box%20sold%20for%20Rs%203%2C000-4%2C000%20last%20year%20while%20a%2025-kg%20box%20fetched%20Rs%202%2C500-3%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%20will%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20bright-red%20and%20glossy%20Washington%20apples%20in%20wholesale%20markets%20to%20Rs%20100%20a%20kilo%2C%20making%20them%20a%20direct%20and%20more%20powerful%20competitor%20for%20local%20apple%20varieties%20which%20are%20dull%20in%20colour%20and%20also%20lack%20lustre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20the%20price%20difference%20between%20imported%20and%20local%20apples.%20The%20quality%20of%20imported%20apples%20is%20exceptionally%20high%20and%20our%20apples%20don%E2%80%99t%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghulam%20Jeelani%20Dar%2C%20an%20apple%20trader%20from%20central%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Ashraf%20Wani%2C%20a%20grower%20from%20Shopian%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20apple%20producing%20districts%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20US%20are%20more%20advanced%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20use%20of%20farming%20technologies%20and%20the%20subsidies%20provided%20by%20their%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20on%20tariff%20will%20hit%20both%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20India%20equally%20as%20the%20domestic%20varieties%20of%20apples%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20Washington%20apple%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Shopian%20Fruit%20Mandi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20traders%20believe%20that%20the%20local%20varieties%20of%20apples%20will%20be%20equally%20in%20high%20demand%20due%20to%20low%20production%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20waiver%20will%20not%20lower%20the%20prices%20of%20local%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20for%20apples%20is%20high%20this%20year%20due%20to%20low%20production.%20Thus%20the%20tariff%20waiver%20on%20imported%20apples%20will%20not%20have%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20local%20producers%20and%20traders%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravinder%20Chauhan%2C%20president%20of%C2%A0%C2%A0Apple%20Growers%20Association%20of%20India%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuty%20policy%20and%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imposes%2035%25%20duty%20and%2015%25%20cess%20on%20apple%20imports%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20tariff%20to%2050%25%20of%20cost%2C%20but%20the%20tariff%20was%20set%20at%2070%25%20in%20case%20of%20the%20US%20apples%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20to%20waive%20off%2020%25%20tariff%20came%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20announced%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20free%20import%20of%20apples%20if%20the%20cost%2C%20insurance%20and%20freight%20(CIF)%20price%20was%20less%20than%20or%20equal%20to%20Rs%2050%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20was%20rolled%20out%20after%20underpriced%20apples%20from%20Iran%20made%20their%20way%20into%20Indian%20markets%20through%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second%20country%20alongside%20Nepal%20to%20enjoy%20duty-free%20trade%20with%20India%2C%20putting%20the%20local%20growers%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20on%20the%20back-foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20of%20many%20growers%20struggling%20to%20recover%20the%20production%20costs%20due%20to%20significantly%20low%20prices%20of%20imported%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImporting%20apples%20is%20not%20a%20wise%20policy%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20the%20trade%20leader%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20home%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20one-fourth%20population%2C%20our%20country%20is%20sufficient%20to%20consume%20the%20local%20production.%20While%20the%20government%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20increase%20tax%20duty%20to%20avoid%20any%20trade%20issues%20with%20the%20US%2C%20it%20can%20increase%20the%20cess%20on%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Japan%20can%20impose%20100%25%20cess%20on%20rice%20imports%20to%20protect%20local%20farmers%2C%20what%20stops%20the%20Union%20government%20from%20taking%20a%20similar%20decision%3F%20The%20increase%20in%20cess%20will%20provide%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20both%20local%20and%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWani%20believes%20that%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20invoke%20CIF%20price%20tag%20on%20imported%20apples%20because%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20tax%20revenue%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20calculated%20decision%20to%20prevent%20tax%20pilferage%20rather%20than%20a%20decision%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20indeed%20concerned%20about%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20farmers%2C%20it%20should%20announce%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20and%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Wani%2C%20the%20grower%20from%20Shopian.%20CIF%20or%20%E2%80%98cost%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20freight%E2%80%99%20are%20charges%20paid%20by%20a%20seller%20for%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBashir%2C%20the%20AVFGDA%20president%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20impose%20100%25%20import%20duty%20on%20imported%20apples%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20protect%20the%20local%20growers%2C%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20apple%20farming%20will%20become%20an%20unsustainable%20practice%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeoples%20Democratic%20Party%20President%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20took%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20urging%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20GOI%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20remove%20additional%20duties%20on%20apples%2C%20walnuts%2C%20and%20almonds%20will%20have%20a%20devastating%20effect%20on%20local%20growers%20in%2